        <mxCell id="t" value="2FA / MFA — Kullanıcı şifresi sızdığında ne yapılabilir?" style="text;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;html=1;fontSize=22;fontStyle=1;align=center;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="40" y="20" width="1720" height="40" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="oA" value="&lt;b&gt;A: Force MFA Re-registration&lt;/b&gt;&#xa;✅ BİZDE VAR" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=15;fontStyle=1;align=center;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="40" y="80" width="420" height="60" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="oAd" value="&lt;b&gt;Ne yapar:&lt;/b&gt; Kullanıcının TÜM MFA yöntemlerini siler&#xa;(Authenticator, telefon, FIDO2, OATH, WHfB, email, TAP).&#xa;Yeniden kayıt olmak zorunda kalır.&#xa;&#xa;&lt;b&gt;Lisans:&lt;/b&gt;  HERKESİN (Free dahil)&#xa;&lt;b&gt;Permission:&lt;/b&gt;  UserAuthenticationMethod.ReadWrite.All&#xa;&lt;b&gt;Graph:&lt;/b&gt;  v1.0 stable&#xa;&lt;b&gt;Etki:&lt;/b&gt;  YÜKSEK — tüm MFA sıfırlanır&#xa;&lt;b&gt;Geri alınabilir mi:&lt;/b&gt;  Hayır (kullanıcı yeniden register)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=14;spacingTop=8;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="40" y="150" width="420" height="270" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="oC" value="&lt;b&gt;C: Confirm Risky&lt;/b&gt;&#xa;✅ BİZDE VAR" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=15;fontStyle=1;align=center;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="480" y="80" width="420" height="60" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="oCd" value="&lt;b&gt;Ne yapar:&lt;/b&gt; Kullanıcıyı 'compromised' işaretler.&#xa;Müşterinin Conditional Access policy'si&#xa;devreye girer (MFA zorlar veya bloklar).&#xa;&#xa;&lt;b&gt;Lisans:&lt;/b&gt;  P1/P2 GEREKLİ&#xa;&lt;b&gt;Permission:&lt;/b&gt;  IdentityRiskyUser.ReadWrite.All&#xa;&lt;b&gt;Graph:&lt;/b&gt;  v1.0 stable&#xa;&lt;b&gt;Etki:&lt;/b&gt;  DÜŞÜK — CA policy'ye bağlı&#xa;&lt;b&gt;Geri alınabilir mi:&lt;/b&gt;  Evet (dismiss)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=14;spacingTop=8;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="480" y="150" width="420" height="270" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="oB" value="&lt;b&gt;B: perUserMfaState&lt;/b&gt;&#xa;❌ REDDETTİK" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;fontSize=15;fontStyle=1;align=center;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="920" y="80" width="420" height="60" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="oBd" value="&lt;b&gt;Ne yapar:&lt;/b&gt; User'a direkt 'MFA enforced' yazar.&#xa;Her login'de MFA zorunlu.&#xa;&#xa;&lt;b&gt;Lisans:&lt;/b&gt;  Free&#xa;&lt;b&gt;Graph:&lt;/b&gt;  BETA ENDPOINT&#xa;&#xa;&lt;b&gt;⚠ Neden REDDETTİK:&lt;/b&gt;&#xa;• Beta = breaking change riski&#xa;• Per-user MFA = legacy model&#xa;• MS Conditional Access'e geçiş yapıyor&#xa;• Bir gün kaldırabilirler" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff;strokeColor=#b85450;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=14;spacingTop=8;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="920" y="150" width="420" height="270" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="oD" value="&lt;b&gt;D: Programmatic CA Policy&lt;/b&gt;&#xa;📋 KARAR BEKLİYOR" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=15;fontStyle=1;align=center;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1360" y="80" width="400" height="60" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="oDd" value="&lt;b&gt;Ne yapar:&lt;/b&gt; User'a özel geçici CA kuralı yazar:&#xa;'bu user sign-in ederse MFA iste'. MFA silmez,&#xa;sadece zorunlu kılar. Geri alınabilir (policy sil).&#xa;&#xa;&lt;b&gt;Lisans:&lt;/b&gt;  P1/P2 GEREKLİ&#xa;&lt;b&gt;Permission:&lt;/b&gt;  Policy.ReadWrite.ConditionalAccess&#xa;&lt;b&gt;Graph:&lt;/b&gt;  v1.0 stable&#xa;&#xa;&lt;b&gt;Avantaj:&lt;/b&gt;  A'dan daha hafif, geri alınabilir&#xa;&lt;b&gt;Dezavantaj:&lt;/b&gt;  P1/P2 gerektiriyor (Free'de yok)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=14;spacingTop=8;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1360" y="150" width="400" height="270" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="guide" value="&lt;b&gt;Hangi müşteriye hangisini öner:&lt;/b&gt;&#xa;&#xa;🏢 Enterprise P1/P2 + CA policy mevcut → C (Confirm Risky) yeter, en hafif&#xa;🏢 Enterprise P1/P2 + CA policy YOK → D (Programmatic CA) — policy biz yazıyoruz (karar verilirse)&#xa;🏠 Küçük firma Free tier → A (Force MFA Re-reg) — tek seçenek, sert ama etkili&#xa;🔒 VIP/kritik compromise → A + disable_account combo — tüm erişimi kes + MFA sıfırla" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#999;fontSize=13;align=left;spacingLeft=14;spacingTop=8;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="40" y="460" width="1720" height="180" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
